serif\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>", "supportInfo": "<p><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">For help related to this&nbsp;<b>call</b>, please contact:&nbsp;</span><font face=\"Arial, sans-serif\">DEFIS-EDF-PROPOSALS@ec.europa.eu</font><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto\"><a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/portal/screen/support/faq;grantAndTendertype=1;categories=p_submission_eval;programme=null;actions=;keyword=;period=null\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">Funding &amp; Tenders Portal FAQ</span></a><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;&#10;color:black\">&nbsp;&ndash; Submission of proposals.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto\"><a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/portal/screen/support/helpdesks/contact-form\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">IT Helpdesk</span></a><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;&#10;color:black\">&nbsp;&ndash; Contact the IT helpdesk for questions such as forgotten passwords, access rights and roles, technical aspects of submission of proposals, etc.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto\"><a href=\"https://webgate.ec.europa.eu/funding-tenders-opportunities/display/OM/Online+Manual\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">Online Manual</span></a><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;&#10;color:black\">&nbsp;&ndash; Step-by-step online guide through the Portal processes from proposal preparation and submission to reporting on your on-going project. Valid for all 2021-2027 programmes.<o:p></o:p></span></p>", "sepTemplate": "<p>To access the Electronic Submission Service, please click on the submission-button next to the <strong>type of action</strong> and the <strong>type of model grant agreement</strong> that corresponds to your proposal. You will then be asked to confirm your choice, as it cannot be changed in the submission system. Upon confirmation, you will be linked to the correct entry point.</p>\r\n<p>To access existing draft proposals for this topic, please login to the Funding &amp; Tenders Portal and select the My Proposals page of the My Area section.</p>", "links": [], "additionalDossiers": [], "infoPackDossiers": [], "callDetailsJSONItem": {"additionalInfo": "", "staticAdditionalInfo": "<p><strong><u>Proposals are invited against any of the following topics</u></strong><strong>:</strong></p><ul level=\"0\"><li><strong>EDF-2022-LS-RA-DIS-AC</strong>: Innovative technologies for adaptive camouflage</li><li><strong>EDF-2022-LS-RA-DIS-EAD</strong>: Electromagnetic artillery demonstrator</li><li><strong>EDF-2022-LS-RA-DIS-NT</strong>: Non-thematic research actions targeting disruptive technologies for defence</li> </ul>\n<p>The Union is considering a contribution of up to EUR 40 000 000 to support proposals addressing the above mentioned topics and their associated objectives, scope, targeted activities, functional requirements and expected impact, while considering a contribution of up to:</p><ul level=\"0\"><li>EUR 15 000 000 to support one or more proposals addressing the topic EDF-2022-LS-RA-DIS-AC</li><li>EUR 15 000 000 to support one or more proposals addressing the topic EDF-2022-LS-RA-DIS-EAD</li><li>EUR 10 000 000 to support proposals addressing the topic EDF-2022-LS-RA-DIS-NT while considering a contribution of up to EUR 4 000 000 per proposal</li> </ul>\n", "latestInfos": [{"approvalDate": "Sep 13, 2022 5:20:31 PM", "lastChangeDate": "Sep 13, 2022 5:20:31 PM", "content": "<p><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#1F497D\">New versions of detailed budget table for EDF LS RA.</span></b><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#1F497D\"> <br />\r\nCorrection of formulas for participation of SMEs and mid-caps in the sheet Info Award criterion 5 (see tab &ldquo;history of changes&rdquo; in the file for more details).</span></p>"}, {"approvalDate": "Aug 11, 2022 1:39:46 PM", "lastChangeDate": "Aug 11, 2022 1:39:46 PM", "content": "<p>Call document updated for removal of limit to participation of research organisations.</p>"}, {"approvalDate": "Jul 5, 2022 10:20:42 AM", "lastChangeDate": "Jul 5, 2022 10:20:42 AM", "content": "<p><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&#10;&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;&#10;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Removal of the fixed subcontracting limit in Section 10.</span></p>"}, {"approvalDate": "Jun 21, 2022 12:57:33 PM", "lastChangeDate": "Jun 21, 2022 12:57:33 PM", "content": "The submission session is now available for: EDF-2022-LS-RA-DIS-AC(EDF-LS), EDF-2022-LS-RA-DIS-EAD(EDF-LS), EDF-2022-LS-RA-DIS-NT(EDF-LS)"}, {"approvalDate": "Jun 10, 2022 3:39:29 PM", "lastChangeDate": "Jun 10, 2022 3:39:29 PM", "content": "<p>Hyperlinks to documents in Topic conditions and documents have been updated.</p>"}], "hasForthcomingTopics": false, "hasOpenTopics": false, "allClosedTopics": true}}}